Re: Help with a couple short audio clips
by Hyperworm » Fri 12.11.2009 10:23 pm 2 is "ga ite".I guess 1 just means "lit upside-down", though I seem to be getting zero results for "sakasa(ma) ni tomoshita" (kanjified various ways), which is confusing me a bit.
