Re: Help with a couple short audio clips
by kurisuto » Fri 12.11.2009 10:45 pm I'd say "he held upside-down a candle that was lit" (i.e "tomoshita rousoku o sakasa ni motte"), but then, it's the first time I've seen "sakasa ni", and I don't really know how it's used.
